{
  "title": "Linux Network Stack - Overview",
  "uid": "linux-network-overview",
  "description": "Operational overview of the Linux network stack via Cloudflare ebpf_exporter (kfree_skb_reason, tcp retransmits, accept latency, interface bytes). NOTE: ebpf_exporter is not yet deployed in this repo; panels will be empty until that exporter is added.",
  "tags": ["ebpf", "networking", "overview"],
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 2,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "label": "Datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to read",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Top row: at-a-glance Golden Signals for the kernel network path (drops, retransmits, new connections, interface throughput).\n\nDrops by reason: which kernel hook called `kfree_skb_reason()` -- non-zero `NO_SOCKET` (2) means traffic to closed ports; `SOCKET_BACKLOG` (17) means apps are not draining accept queues fast enough; `TCP_INVALID_SEQUENCE` (35) means reordering or loss.\n\nTCP retransmits + accept latency p99 isolate whether problems are on the wire or in the application.\n\nInterface throughput is sourced from `node_exporter` (`node_network_*`) so it is available even without the eBPF exporter.\n\nData source: Cloudflare `ebpf_exporter` (kfree_skb, tcp_retransmit, tcp_connect_latency probes). Not yet deployed -- ebpf_* panels will be empty until then."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Network Health Summary",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 24, "h": 1},
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Packet Drop Rate",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 10},
              {"color": "red", "value": 100}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "pps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(ebpf_exporter_packet_drops[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "TCP Retransmit Rate",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 6, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 50}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "cps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(ebpf_exporter_tcp_retransmits[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "New TCP Connections",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "cps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(ebpf_exporter_tcp_connections[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Interface Throughput (RX+TX)",
      "description": "Sum of received + transmitted bytes across all non-virtual interfaces from node_exporter.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 18, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "unit": "Bps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*|cali.*|cilium.*|cni.*|flannel.*|tunl.*\"}[$__rate_interval])) + sum(rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*|cali.*|cilium.*|cni.*|flannel.*|tunl.*\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Packet Drops",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 9, "w": 24, "h": 1},
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Packet Drops by Reason",
      "description": "Per-reason drop rate from kfree_skb_reason(). Reason codes are the Linux SKB_DROP_REASON_* enum.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 16, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal"}
          },
          "unit": "pps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"},
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true,
          "values": ["value", "max", "mean"]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (reason) (rate(ebpf_exporter_packet_drops[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "Reason {{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Drop Distribution (current window)",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 16, "y": 10, "w": 8, "h": 8},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "pieType": "donut"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (reason) (increase(ebpf_exporter_packet_drops[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "TCP Performance",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 1},
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "TCP Retransmits",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic", "fixedColor": "red"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 70
          },
          "unit": "cps"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(ebpf_exporter_tcp_retransmits[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "retransmits/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "TCP Connection Rate",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "unit": "cps"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(ebpf_exporter_tcp_connections[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "new connections/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Accept Latency p50 / p99",
      "description": "Histogram quantiles derived from ebpf_exporter_accept_latency_seconds_bucket. Rising p99 with stable p50 means tail-latency in accept() -- usually a saturated application thread pool.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 25, "w": 24, "h": 7},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(ebpf_exporter_accept_latency_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(ebpf_exporter_accept_latency_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Interface Throughput",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 32, "w": 24, "h": 1},
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "RX Bandwidth by Interface",
      "description": "node_exporter node_network_receive_bytes_total, excluding loopback and common virtual/CNI interfaces.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 33, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 30
          },
          "unit": "Bps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "values": ["value", "max"]}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (instance, device) (rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*|cali.*|cilium.*|cni.*|flannel.*|tunl.*\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}} {{device}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "TX Bandwidth by Interface",
      "description": "node_exporter node_network_transmit_bytes_total, excluding loopback and common virtual/CNI interfaces.",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 33, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 30
          },
          "unit": "Bps"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"},
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "values": ["value", "max"]}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (instance, device) (rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|docker.*|veth.*|cali.*|cilium.*|cni.*|flannel.*|tunl.*\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}} {{device}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
